Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Leased to ASX and National tenant

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Quinlan Property are pleased to offer 2 Greg Jabs Drive, Mt Louisa to the market. This is a rare opportunity to secure a multi-tenanted facility leased to an ASX and National tenants.

Features of the investment include:
* 1,964sqm Building area
* 5,366sqm Prominent corner site
* $258,871 Net annual income
* Two buildings on two individual lots
* Buildings contain showroom, office and warehouse areas
* Allied Pinnacle have been in the property for over 20 years
* Total Eden have been in the property for over 12 years
* Leased to an ASX and National tenant

Perfectly situated along the major arterial route of Bayswater Road, the assets benefit from significant traffic exposure whilst being placed in the high trading commercial and retail precinct of Mt. Louisa. The property is located approximately 6.5km south west of the Townsville Central Business District and located directly behind the region’s major shopping centre, Domain Central Shopping Centre.

This property can be can be purchased individually or in one line with 1 Greg Jabs Drive.

For Sale by Expressions of Interest Closing 4pm Wednesday 16 May 2018.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact the Exclusive Agents.

CBRE and Quinlan Property are pleased to offer 1 Greg Jabs Drive, Mt Louisa to the market. This is a rare opportunity to secure a first class facility leased to a Wesfarmers tenant.

Features of the investment include:
* 2,788sqm Building area
* 6,264sqm Prominent corner site
* $246,467 Net annual income 
* Versatile showroom, office and warehouse facility
* Blackwoods have been in the property for over 12 years
* Tenant is owned by ASX listed Wesfarmers

Perfectly situated along the major arterial route of Bayswater Road, the assets benefit from significant traffic exposure whilst being placed in the high trading commercial and retail precinct of Mt. Louisa. The property is located approximately 6.5km south west of the Townsville Central Business District and located directly behind the region’s major shopping centre, Domain Central Shopping Centre.

The property can be purchased individually or in one line with 2 Greg Jabs Drive. 

For Sale by Expressions of Interest Closing 4pm Wednesday 16 May 2018.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact the Exclusive Agents.

Under instruction from J P Cronin and W J Harris of McGrathNichol as receivers and managers. This is an outstanding opportunity to purchase a multi-tenanted industrial investment with great growth potential. The 5 buildings are built over 2 titles with a very low 18% site coverage. The local Townsville economy strengthens the future upside of this investment.

For more information please contact Edward Bull on 0438 619 692 or Aaron Bates on 0410 650 663.
